Quickstrike:

 

 

Quickstrike glared up at the big toad-bot. If he had to ablity, he would sneer. He didn't like him. His crimson optics had a firm stare on him for a while, then he looked away. He didn't even bother to pay attention to Dark Mouse. He was angry about being locked up. He was mad at Black Arachnia and he wanted answers.
